				<text><![CDATA[Dear Customer,

Adventist Health Hong Kong aims to provide the very best medical services and facilities. You are important to us and we care about your comfort and the way you are treated while you are in our care.

Our hospital has designed a special program with you, the patient, in mind. Entitled <style forecolor='#cc0066'>SHARE</style>, this program involves us making the following promises to you:

         <style forecolor='#cc0066'>S</style> – Sense people’s needs before they ask
         <style forecolor='#cc0066'>H</style> – Help each other
         <style forecolor='#cc0066'>A</style> – Acknowledge people’s feelings
         <style forecolor='#cc0066'>R</style> – Respect the dignity and privacy of others
         <style forecolor='#cc0066'>E</style> – Explain what is happening

We would like to know exactly what you think about our hospital, in aspects of our services, facilities, and staff. Your comments on the things you like and the areas which we can improve are of utmost importance to us.

Please take a few moments to scan the specific QR code for you below and fill out the feedback form.

Adventist Health Hong Kong is committed to excellence – not just our idea of excellence, but your ideas as well.]]></text>
